title: Vogue India - December 2017 (gnv64)
description: Vogue India - December 2017 English | 376 pages | True PDF | 103 mb Before it's in fashion, it's in Vogue. Everything you need to know about fashion, trends, beauty, people and lifestyle, VOGUE India is your ultimate style guide. In these pages you’ll find the hottest, newest and latest from the world of fashion and beyond, both in India and from across the world, making it the must-have accessory for the modern, fashionable Indian woman. Anyone who has seen Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif together will tell you that their conversations make for an interesting play of contrasting personalities. Don’t believe me? Just read our cover story, where features editor Megha Mahindru plays witness to their banter on set. This December marks a wrap-up of our 10th anniversary celebrations at Vogue India. No doubt, this has been a landmark year for us— from kicking off the first edition of Vogueathon this January, to finding a cover girl in model-of the-moment Kendall Jenner in May. And the year only got bigger and better. In August, our annual Vogue Beauty Awards set the bar high by bringing together the entire Bachchan family, while September ended with the biggest event we’ve hosted till date—our first-ever Vogue Women of the Year awards. Catch all the action on pg 222. https://s2.postimg.org/t6dvz08d5/Vogue_India_-_December_2017.jpg
